+| 1 | Adapter handles scaffold (`adapter.rs`) + `AgentContextHandle::load()` wiring | None — can start immediately |
+| 2 | `JournalHandle::append_hand_entry()` wiring in `PipeMode::handle_action()` | Slice 1 |
